data.description: Looking for a home with great curb appeal, comfortable design & tons of room? Live large in this spacious home w/tons of room to stretch! With lovely mature landscaping in a phenomenal neighborhood, you’ll fall instantly in love upon pulling into the driveway. With 5 bedrooms, including one on the mail level, there’s more than enough room for everyone! Cook the perfect meal for friends & family in your well-appointed kitchen w/ample counter space, island, corner pantry, & tons of storage; or cozy up next to the gas fireplace for a quiet night at home getting lost in a good book. Head upstairs to slip away & recharge in the massive master retreat w/vaulted ceilings, dual vanities, big soaker tub, walk-in shower, & large walk-in closet. Sizable bedrooms throughout, and the 2nd full bathroom also features dual vanities, a garden tub. Head out back to throw the ball for fido then sit under the covered patio to stay cool in the summer! A 3-car garage allows for ample storage opportunities!
